s://lih.kg/1885602\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1885602</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:48:40.000Z","msg":"周圍恐嚇人"},{"pid":"eb7297c070647cac587b3ae4d367630660d30daf","tid":1885793,"uid":315833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:51:04.000Z","msg":"垃圾到咁，凶完人又要淆底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e1327216165e34baf5222468893342c0ac115d2","tid":1885793,"uid":241069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"成班垃圾 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72e46a47506ee6a85fca2fc43a772370de3f6855","tid":1885793,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:51:50.000Z","msg":"警荒"},{"pid":"d17e7087534ce8db23d0a48b8a44605bb820eb7f","tid":1885793,"uid":68097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:52:01.000Z","msg":"警謊"},{"pid":"d35b92eb64af7e4afc3b29ee314e1d585d4520ca","tid":1885793,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:52:42.000Z","msg":"黑警睇你唔順眼殺完你掉落海都得<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a485080c1100a4bbda6fc0b5687ab1dc6b93cc5e","tid":1885793,"uid":123988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94fa69f8b21b2f4ae12758dd8732a6b47b57d289","tid":1885793,"uid":322732,"like":69,"dislike":0,"score":69,"quote":{"pid":"fa7b7cb94017fa243bb3694776ac5cfedfc8e76e","tid":1885793,"uid":78243,"like":82,"dislike":0,"score":82,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T14:05:57.000Z","